<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>月下荷花 ——花中仙子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/青衣小生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八月池塘画中仙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一叶撑起半边天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皎月当空柔情比</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长夜同寄岁平安</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.8.19 蔡国生/青衣小生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200821/079ea540f1604154be301b8cafec7bfb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《竹》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/青衣小生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风吹竹影见微光</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
